General.Name: Hydrogen Hybrid Technologies Inc
General.Description: Hydrogen Hybrid Technologies, Inc. manufactures, sales and distributes on-board hydrogen generating and injections systems for the original equipment manufacturers in car and light truck markets. Its on-board hydrogen generating system improves fuel consumption and reduces pollution through the enhancement of the internal combustion process. This technology consists of an on-board system, which generates hydrogen and oxygen by splitting distilled water. In addition, the company holds rights to distribute the product to other markets, including the heavy goods vehicle market. Hydrogen Hybrid Technologies, Inc. is based in Pickering, Canada.
